UEFA backs Turkish referee Cüneyt Çakır over his controversial decision to red card Manchester United's Nani in last night's elimination by a 2–1 scoreline (3–2 on aggregate) at the feet of Real Madrid in the second leg of their 2012–13 UEFA Champions League last 16 tie at Old Trafford. (The Guardian) (The Independent)In golf, American golfer Phil Mickelson wins the 2013 Open Championship at Muirfield in Scotland for the first time. (Al-Jazeera), (AP via The Washington Post)